---
title: Savoury Sheet Pan Chicken with Roasted Veg and Pan Gravy
description: Nothing says comfort food like pan-roasted chicken and a hearty veggie medley of broccoli, potatoes and onions, all drizzled in a rich pan sauce. You'll be licking your plate clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-sur-la-plaque-46d54ac7.jpg
